Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:33.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也有虛海無限延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:39.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉浸在銀色的溫柔中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:44.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}現在開始睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:50.69,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:56.16,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直尋找着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:24:01.70,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人的溫暖
